{"tid":1561001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新屋嶺黑警虐待被補人士fact check","createTime":"2019-09-11T12:11:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T12:44:40.000Z","uid":99883,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f26f815f5e31e0b00893e61f946c393f9b48dd27","tid":1561001,"uid":99883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:11:55.000Z","msg":"fact check其實唔一定要有記者，拍片，或者目擊者，我舉一個例子：<br />\n<br />\n有一間博物館展覽一件古董，間博物館只有一個出入口，冇其他缺口或者秘道可以入到黎，職員只會係博物館外看守。呢間博物館每次只容許一個人參觀，而每位參觀者離開後，職員就會望一望確保古董仲係度完好無損。<br />\n<br />\n假設得你入完出返黎，件古董就發現爛左，撇除天災同職員監守自盜，除左你之外仲有其他人會整爛件古董咩？仲駛唔駛影住你整爛既過程？<br />\n<br />\n新屋嶺就係類似既情況，入去時冇穿冇爛，入到出返黎就全身骨折，唔係黑警所為仲有咩可能性？驗傷都驗到係咩導致咁既傷勢"},{"pid":"eb6f4957c0c388d6b5f14c49e886faf0c0881a13","tid":1561001,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:12:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"278e5127d0d342094075b7259d3c59c97fec4df2","tid":1561001,"uid":178013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:12:56.000Z","msg":"【捍衛香港 存亡之秋】915民陣遊行攻略<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1560996\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1560996</a>"},{"pid":"673a74b8600b967a6a7f8043a124cedc7fe680ae","tid":1561001,"uid":56305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s